title: [RG.REBOOT] Cube World Alpha 3
description:
Game Notes 
~~~~~~~~~~~
A main feature of Cube World is the random world generation. In contrast to many games, worlds 
are not designed by a level designer, but generated procedurally by the game using math and random 
numbers. The result is an endless world (nearly endless, i.e. players can't reach the borders), so 
players can explore new landscapes all the time.
